---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="jornada-laboral"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-workhours"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--wide wheat-px-6 wheat-w-full">
        <div class="wheat-text-center wheat-mb-16">
            <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-workhours-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block wheat-mb-4">
                El Coste del Progreso
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-workhours-title mb-6">La Jornada Laboral</h2>
            <p class="wheat-text-lg wheat-workhours-desc wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="La promesa de la agricultura era la seguridad, pero el precio fue el tiempo libre."
                />
                Contrario a la creencia popular, la vida "primitiva" no era una lucha constante.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-items-end wheat-workhours-chart">
            <div class="wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-justify-end wheat-h-full wheat-workhours-group">
                <div class="wheat-mb-4 wheat-text-center wheat-workhours-tooltip">
                    <span class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-font-bold wheat-workhours-val wheat-workhours-val--hunter">~3-5 horas</span>
                    <p class="wheat-text-xs wheat-workhours-label wheat-workhours-label--hunter wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-widest wheat-mt-1">
                        Subsistencia
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-w-full wheat-workhours-bar wheat-workhours-bar--hunter">
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-workhours-bar-bg wheat-workhours-bar-bg--hunter"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-workhours-bar-line wheat-workhours-bar-line--hunter"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="wheat-mt-4 wheat-text-center">
                    <h3 class="wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-workhours-group-title">Cazador-Recolector</h3>
                    <p class="wheat-text-sm wheat-workhours-group-desc wheat-mt-2">
                        Tiempo libre abundante. Trabajo intermitente.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-justify-end wheat-h-full wheat-workhours-group">
                <div class="wheat-mb-4 wheat-text-center wheat-workhours-tooltip">
                    <span class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-font-bold wheat-workhours-val wheat-workhours-val--farmer">~9-10 horas</span>
                    <p class="wheat-text-xs wheat-workhours-label wheat-workhours-label--farmer wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-widest wheat-mt-1">
                        De sol a sol
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-w-full wheat-workhours-bar wheat-workhours-bar--farmer">
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-workhours-bar-bg wheat-workhours-bar-bg--farmer"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-workhours-bar-line wheat-workhours-bar-line--farmer"></div>
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-workhours-bar-overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="wheat-mt-4 wheat-text-center">
                    <h3 class="wheat-text-xl wheat-font-bold wheat-workhours-group-title">Agricultor Neolítico</h3>
                    <p class="wheat-text-sm wheat-workhours-group-desc wheat-mt-2">
                        Trabajo constante. Preparación de suelo, siembra, cosecha, molienda.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-mt-16 wheat-text-center">
            <p class="wheat-text-xs wheat-workhours-source wheat-italic">
                Datos basados en estudios de Marshall Sahlins ("La sociedad opulenta primitiva") y
                registros antropológicos de sociedades !Kung.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-workhours {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-chapter {
        color: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.6);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-chart {
        height: 50vh;
        align-items: flex-end;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-workhours-chart {
            height: 400px;
        }
    }
    .wheat-workhours-group {
        height: 100%;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-tooltip {
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-group:hover .wheat-workhours-tooltip {
        opacity: 1;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-val--hunter {
        color: #34d399;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-val--farmer {
        color: #f59e0b;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-label--hunter {
        color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.6);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-label--farmer {
        color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.6);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar {
        background-color: #292524;
        border-top-left-radius: 0.5rem;
        border-top-right-radius: 0.5rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: all 1s ease-out;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-group:hover .wheat-workhours-bar {
        background-color: #44403c;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar--hunter {
        height: 35%;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar--farmer {
        height: 90%;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar-bg--hunter {
        background-color: rgba(6, 95, 70, 0.2);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar-bg--farmer {
        background-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.2);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar-line--hunter {
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar-line--farmer {
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-workhours-bar-overlay {
        opacity: 0.2;
        mix-blend-mode: overlay;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-group-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-group-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-workhours-source {
        color: #57534e;
    }
</style>
